This is a beautiful trail perfect for a walk, run, or bike ride. The trail is well maintained and works well for jogging strollers, mountain, or hybrid bikes. The first about 2 miles from this trailhead is spent mostly along rivers and ponds and there are a few benches and spots to stop for a break or to enjoy the scenery. There are several road crossings necessary to fully navigate the trail, so please use caution.

